<P>
 Over the past several years my interest in baseball has been declining with 
the exception of the playoffs and World Series. The past weeks I have been 
watching the PBS series "Baseball" on KCET and it brought back a flood of good 
memories of when I played in my youth. I hope today's baseball players were 
watching so they can witness firsthand what they well might ruin. 
</P>
<P>
