 After having returned to TV viewing last season because of enjoyable sitcoms 
such as "Wings," "Home Improvement," "Frasier," "John Larroquette" and "Grace 
Under Fire," I am totally dismayed by this season's lineup. It places these 
shows right on top of each other and there is no way I can enjoy all of my 
favorites. 
</P>
