<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA101694-0083 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 089052 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 16, 1994, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
