<DOCNO> LA101694-0257 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 089226 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 16, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Opinion; Part M; Page 4; Column 4; Editorial Writers Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
