<DOCNO> LA101694-0301 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 089270 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 16, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
