<DATE>
<P>
October 16, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 3; Column 5; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
1368 words 
