<P>
 Because of an editing error it was implied that Africanized Honeybees have 
been detected in Imperial County.Their presence is suspected, however, since 
they have been noticed in Yuma, Ariz., only three miles from the California 
border. Africanized bees have "hitchhiked" to California several times, most 
recently in July on a freighter entering the L.A. harbor from Guatemala. 
</P>
