 In a development in restrictions on the use of laundry soap to kill insects, 
Veda Federighi, assistant communications director of the California 
Environmental Protection Agency's Department of Pesticide Regulations, says 
that the department has registered an insecticidal soap product named M-Pede to 
be used against bee swarms by police officers, firefighters and other 
professionals only. 
