<HEADLINE>
<P>
STATION PARKING RULES SENSELESS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 What kind of mentality came up with the brilliant idea of three-hour parking 
at the Fullerton Amtrak station? One cannot even take the train to Santa Ana 
and back to Fullerton in three hours. 
</P>
<P>
 The multilevel parking structure also has three-hour spaces and 72-hour 
