clean. Aren't these two issues that environmentalists are always blathering 
about? 
</P>
<P>
 I have a solution: Completely restructure the entire Transportation Center 
parking by using some common sense and getting rid of all the three-hour 
parking inside the structure. It relates to nothing. 
</P>
<P>
